---
title: Smoky Chicken Fajitas with Charred Pepper and Onions, with Lime Crema
description: Fajitas are the ultimate crowd-pleaser, especially with fixings as delicious as these. We’re upping the ante with our custom Southwest Spice Blend and an unbeatable lime crema. This will be a fajita night to remember.
